Package: dairynasem
Type: Package
Title: Wrapper functions to run the NASEM (2021) dairy nutritional model
Version: 0.1.0
Author: MaryGrace Erickson
Maintainer: MaryGrace Erickson <eric3085@umn.edu>
Description: This package is designed for dairy nutrition researchers to efficiently run the NASEM 2021 dairy nutritional model. This package simplifies the process of running simulations on multiple animal and diet inputs.
